  "texts": [
    "However, if a human rephrases the same text multiple times, the output should indicate that the response is generated by a human.",
    "Thus, we aim to incorporate and integrate these effects into our methodology.",
    "To achieve this, we compute the energy associated with each perturbed text embedding and average it.",
    "Then, we integrate this averaged energy with Binary Cross Entropy (BCE) loss of the model function to have an effective total loss.",
    "Through optimization of this loss function, we are able to compute distinct energies for human-generated text and ChatGPT-generated text."
  ],
